{
  "id": null,
  "title": "MarketSage - Error Correlation & Analysis",
  "tags": ["marketsage", "errors", "correlation", "debugging"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "üö® Error Rate Overview",
      "type": "stat",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(traces_spanmetrics_calls_total{status_code=\"STATUS_CODE_ERROR\"}[5m])) / sum(rate(traces_spanmetrics_calls_total[5m])) * 100",
          "datasource": "Prometheus"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 0},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "thresholds": {
            "steps": [
              {"color": "green", "value": 0},
              {"color": "yellow", "value": 1},
              {"color": "orange", "value": 5},
              {"color": "red", "value": 10}
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "üìà Error Trend",
      "type": "sparkline",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(traces_spanmetrics_calls_total{status_code=\"STATUS_CODE_ERROR\"}[5m]))",
          "datasource": "Prometheus"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 0},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "rps",
          "color": {"mode": "single", "fixedColor": "red"}
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "üîß Active Error Types",
      "type": "stat",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "count(count by (service_name, span_name) (rate(traces_spanmetrics_calls_total{status_code=\"STATUS_CODE_ERROR\"}[5m]) > 0))",
          "datasource": "Prometheus"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 0},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "color": {"mode": "single", "fixedColor": "orange"}
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "‚è±Ô∏è Time to Recovery",
      "type": "stat",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "time() - on() group_left() max by () (timestamp(changes(up{job=\"marketsage-web\"}[1h]) > 0))",
          "datasource": "Prometheus"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 0},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "dtdurations",
          "color": {"mode": "single", "fixedColor": "blue"}
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "title": "üîç Error Correlation Matrix",
      "type": "table",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (service_name, span_name, status_code) (rate(traces_spanmetrics_calls_total{status_code=\"STATUS_CODE_ERROR\"}[5m]))",
          "format": "table",
          "datasource": "Prometheus"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 4},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "rps",
          "custom": {
            "displayMode": "color-background",
            "align": "center"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "steps": [
              {"color": "green", "value": 0},
              {"color": "yellow", "value": 0.01},
              {"color": "orange", "value": 0.1},
              {"color": "red", "value": 1}
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "title": "üìä Error Distribution by Service",
      "type": "piechart",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (service_name) (rate(traces_spanmetrics_calls_total{status_code=\"STATUS_CODE_ERROR\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{service_name}}",
          "datasource": "Prometheus"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 4},
      "options": {
        "pieType": "pie",
        "legend": {"displayMode": "visible", "placement": "right"}
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "title": "üîó Cross-Service Error Propagation",
      "type": "nodeGraph",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "traces_service_graph_request_failed_total",
          "datasource": "Prometheus"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": {"h": 10, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 12},
      "options": {
        "nodes": {
          "mainStatUnit": "rps",
          "secondaryStatUnit": "percent"
        },
        "edges": {
          "mainStatUnit": "rps",
          "secondaryStatUnit": "percent"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "title": "üìù Recent Error Logs",
      "type": "logs",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "{service_name=\"unknown_service\"} |~ \"(?i)error|exception|fail|500|400\" | json",
          "datasource": "Loki"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 22},
      "options": {
        "showTime": true,
        "showLabels": true,
        "showCommonLabels": false,
        "wrapLogMessage": true,
        "prettifyLogMessage": true,
        "enableLogDetails": true,
        "dedupStrategy": "exact",
        "sortOrder": "Descending"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "title": "üéØ Error Timeline Correlation",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (service_name) (rate(traces_spanmetrics_calls_total{status_code=\"STATUS_CODE_ERROR\"}[1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{service_name}} errors/sec",
          "datasource": "Prometheus"
        },
        {
          "expr": "rate(container_cpu_usage_seconds_total{id=~\"/docker/.*\"}[1m]) * 100",
          "legendFormat": "CPU: {{id}}",
          "datasource": "Prometheus"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 22},
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "min": 0
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byRegexp", "options": "/.*errors.*/"},
            "properties": [
              {"id": "unit", "value": "rps"},
              {"id": "custom.axisPlacement", "value": "left"},
              {"id": "color", "value": {"mode": "palette-classic"}}
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": {"id": "byRegexp", "options": "/CPU.*/"},
            "properties": [
              {"id": "unit", "value": "percent"},
              {"id": "custom.axisPlacement", "value": "right"},
              {"id": "color", "value": {"mode": "single", "fixedColor": "blue"}}
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "title": "üî¨ Error Analysis & Actions",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 30},
      "options": {
        "content": "## üö® Error Analysis Dashboard\n\n### üéØ **Quick Actions:**\n- **Red zones** = immediate investigation needed\n- **Error spikes** correlating with **CPU/Memory** spikes = resource issues\n- **Cross-service errors** = check dependencies\n- **Database errors** = check queries and connections\n\n### üîç **Investigation Workflow:**\n1. **Check Error Rate** - > 5% needs immediate attention\n2. **Identify Service** - Which service has highest error rate?\n3. **Check Correlation** - Are errors related to resource usage?\n4. **Review Logs** - Click on error logs for detailed context\n5. **Trace Analysis** - Use Tempo to see full request flow\n\n### üõ†Ô∏è **Common Root Causes:**\n- **Database**: Connection timeouts, slow queries\n- **Memory**: Memory leaks, GC pressure\n- **Network**: Service unavailability, timeouts\n- **Business Logic**: Validation errors, data issues",
        "mode": "markdown"
      }
    }
  ],
  "time": {"from": "now-1h", "to": "now"},
  "refresh": "30s",
  "version": 1,
  "editable": true
}